field.div:

Dear ${object.responsible_id.name},

Your personal sales target has been closed with the following results:


Description: ${object.name}

Target Amount: ${object.target_amount} ${object.currency_id.name}

Achieved Amount: ${object.achieved_amount} ${object.currency_id.name}

Achievement: ${object.percent_achieved}%

Period: ${object.date_start} to ${object.date_end}

                % if object.percent_achieved >= 100:

Congratulations! You have achieved your target!
                % else:

Thank you for your efforts. Keep striving for the next target!
                % endif

Sales Management Team

Dear ${object.responsible_id.name},
Here's an update on your personal sales target:
Description: ${object.name}
Target Amount: ${object.target_amount} ${object.currency_id.name}
Achieved Amount: ${object.achieved_amount} ${object.currency_id.name}
Achievement: ${object.percent_achieved}%
Theoretical Achievement: ${object.theoretical_percent}%
Period: ${object.date_start} to ${object.date_end}
% if object.theoretical_status == 'completed':
Congratulations! You have achieved your target! Keep it up! % elif object.theoretical_status == 'on_track':
You are on track to meet your target. Keep up the good work! % elif object.theoretical_status == 'below':
You are below the theoretical target. Consider increasing your efforts. % endif
Sales Management Team


Dear ${object.responsible_id.name},

A team sales target has been closed with the following results:


Description: ${object.name}

Teams: ${object.team_ids}

Target Amount: ${object.target_amount} ${object.currency_id.name}

Achieved Amount: ${object.achieved_amount} ${object.currency_id.name}

Achievement: ${object.percent_achieved}%

Period: ${object.date_start} to ${object.date_end}

                % if object.percent_achieved >= 100:

Congratulations! The team has achieved the target!
                % else:

Thank you for the team's efforts. Keep striving for the next target!
                % endif

Sales Management Team

Dear ${object.responsible_id.name},
Here's an update on the team sales target:
Description: ${object.name}
Teams: ${object.team_ids}
Target Amount: ${object.target_amount} ${object.currency_id.name}
Achieved Amount: ${object.achieved_amount} ${object.currency_id.name}
Achievement: ${object.percent_achieved}%
Theoretical Achievement: ${object.theoretical_percent}%
Period: ${object.date_start} to ${object.date_end}
% if object.theoretical_status == 'completed':
Congratulations! The team has achieved the target! Keep it up! % elif object.theoretical_status == 'on_track':
The team is on track to meet the target. Keep up the good work! % elif object.theoretical_status == 'below':
The team is below the theoretical target. Consider increasing efforts. % endif
Sales Management Team
